item.title: ETSHelper
item.description: See https://github.com/CzzzzH/ETSHelper Introduction The bot is based on Nonebot (A asynchronous framework of QQ chatbot) and Jittor (A Just-in-time(JIT) deep learning framework). The former provides communication services for the bot , and the latter helps crack captcha on the website. Usage You need construct dataset with captcha data on the official test registration website and install Jittor. Then train the model. Start to get GRE/TOEFL test seats status with gre_seat.
